<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fire-n">fire <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'faɪə(r)/    美 /'faɪər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 火</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Fire and water may be good servants, but bad masters.
水火可以成为忠仆，用之不慎则是灾主。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is no smoke without fire. 
无风不起浪。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 火灾；失火：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>fight a fire</strong> 
救火</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A <strong>fire broke out</strong> last night at his house.
昨晚他家失火了。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 炉火；炭火：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>make a fire</strong>
生火</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Sam had <strong>lit a fire</strong> to welcome us home.
萨姆点燃炉火欢迎我们回家。</p></div>

<h4 id="4-u">4.★ <strong>[U] 射击；炮火；火力：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The gunmen <strong>opened fire on</strong> the police.
持枪歹徒向警察开枪。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="catch-fire">catch fire</h3>
<p>1.<strong>着火：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The basement caught fire by accident.
地下室意外着火了。</p><footer>2014 天津</footer></div>

<h3 id="on-fire">on fire</h3>
<p>1.<strong>着火；火辣辣：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His clothes were on fire.
他的衣服着火了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I stood frozen as ice, but my face was on fire. I wanted to get into a hole and hide.
我呆呆地站着，脸上火辣辣的，恨不能找个洞躲进去。</p><footer>2008 全国</footer></div>

<h3 id="play-with-fire">play with fire</h3>
<p>1.<strong>玩火</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="set-on-fire-set-fire-to">set ... on fire / set fire to</h3>
<p>1.<strong>使…燃烧；放火烧：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>A cigarette end set the house on fire.
一根烟蒂点燃了这所房子。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Police believe that someone set fire to the factory deliberately.
警方认为有人故意纵火烧工厂。</p></div></div>